   Heading: Non-OCRWM Documents

   A Roadmap for Developing Accelerator Transmutation of Waste (ATW)
   Technology: A Report to Congress (October 1999)

   USGS Circular 1184 "Yucca Mountain as a Radioactive-Waste Repository"

   Heading: Contractor System Studies
     * View the Cost Escalation and Interest Rates (October 2001) which
       supplies cost escalation rates that will be used in subsequent
       documents for converting year-of-expenditure costs to constant 2001
       dollars for the CRWMS program and also provides forecasts of
       several different interest rates, which can be used for analysis
       purposes.

     * View the Independent Cost Estimate (ICE) Review of the CRWM Program
       2001 TSLCC (January 2001). In support of the Site Recommendation
       Consideration Report (SRCR) and The Total System Life Cycle Cost
       Estimate (2001 TSLCC), Burns and Roe was contracted by the DOE to
       perform a review of the TSLCC.

     * View the Independent Cost Estimate (ICE) Review of the CRWM Program
       2001 Modular Design/Construction and Operation Options Report
       (April 2001). Burns and Roe was tasked to review and comment on the
       report titled CRWMS Modular Design/Construction and Operation
       Options Report (Rev.3) see below.



